reg_info.full_title: O. Reg. 754/92: FEE FOR DISHONOURED CHEQUES
reg_info.act_under: Financial Administration Act   Loi sur l’administration financière

content.content: 1. For the purpose of section 8.1 of the Act, the fee in respect of a cheque that the drawee refuses to cash is $35. O. Reg. 754/92, s. 1.
content.raw_html: 1. For the purpose of section 8.1 of the Act, the fee in respect of a cheque that the drawee refuses to cash is $35. O. Reg. 754/92, s. 1.

content.content: 2. Omitted (provides for coming into force of provisions of this Regulation). O. Reg. 754/92, s. 2.
